title: Beautiful 2 bedroom home available now! Cats & Dogs welcome!
posting_body: ['Fantastic location with a large apartment, great price and pet friendly.', 'Located across the street from Islands of Peace Park which is located on the Mississippi river.', 'From Island of Peace park trails, you can connect with the Minneapolis bike trail system which includes the Grand Rounds National Scenic Byway.', 'This apartment building is also one block from the NorthStar rail station, which is the last NorthStar station before downtown Minneapolis.', 'Your commute will never be easier!', 'We also have free off-street parking and on-site laundry for residents.', 'We welcome cats and small dogs at this building.', 'Please contact the office at', 'show contact info', 'to set up an apartment showing our to apply go to our website at <URL>', '190 Island Park Dr NE is an apartment located in Anoka County and the 55432 ZIP Code.']
